                "description": "## Purpose\nList menu categories.\n\n## Endpoint\n- **Method:** `GET`\n- **URL:** `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/menu/categories/`\n\n> **Base URL (local dev):** `http://127.0.0.1:8000`\n\n## Authentication\nNone (or as configured by collection).\n\n## Query parameters\nNone.\n\n## Response\n**200 OK** (paginated list)\n\n### Schema\n```json\n{\n  \"count\": 0,\n  \"next\": null,\n  \"previous\": null,\n  \"results\": []\n}\n```\n\n- `count` *(number)*: Total number of categories.\n- `next` *(string|null)*: URL to the next page of results, if any.\n- `previous` *(string|null)*: URL to the previous page of results, if any.\n- `results` *(array)*: List of category objects (shape depends on API implementation).\n\n### Example response\n```json\n{\n  \"count\": 0,\n  \"next\": null,\n  \"previous\": null,\n  \"results\": []\n}\n```"
