                "description": "## Purpose\nCreate a new **menu item** for a restaurant.\n\n## Authentication\nRequires a valid **Bearer token**.\n\nHeader:\n```http\nAuthorization: Bearer {{access_token}}\n```\n\n## Endpoint\n```http\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/menu/categories/\n```\n\n## Request body (JSON)\nSend a JSON object with the following fields:\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---:|:---:|---|\n| `restaurant` | integer | Yes | Restaurant ID that this menu item belongs to. |\n| `category` | integer | Yes | Category ID to group the menu item under. |\n| `name` | string | Yes | Display name of the menu item. |\n| `description` | string | No | Short description of the menu item. |\n| `price` | string/decimal | Yes | Price of the item (often represented as a decimal string). |\n| `is_available` | boolean | No | Whether the item is currently available. |\n\n## Example request\n```http\nPOST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/menu/categories/\nAuthorization: Bearer {{access_token}}\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\"restaurant\":1,\"category\":1,\"name\":\"Margherita Pizza\",\"description\":\"Classic tomato and cheese\",\"price\":\"12.99\",\"is_available\":true}\n```\n\n## Success response\n**201 Created**\n\n```json\n{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"Margherita Pizza\",\"image\":null}\n```\n\n## Common error responses\n- **400 Bad Request** — Validation error (missing/invalid fields, incorrect types, etc.).\n- **401 Unauthorized** — Missing/expired/invalid Bearer token.\n- **403 Forbidden** — Authenticated but not allowed (insufficient permissions / not allowed to create items for the given restaurant).\n"
              },
